<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.9">
<l>tāymār mōrviṟkap pōvar tamappaṉmār kaṟṟā niṟaippiṉ pupōvar</l>
<l>nīyāyp pāṭi yiḷaṅkaṉṉi mārkaḷai nērpaṭa vēkoṇṭu pōti</l>
<l>kāyvārk keṉṟu mukappaṉa vēceytu kaṇṭār kaḻaṟat tiriyum</l>
<l>āyā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Their] mothers go to sell buttermilk.</l>
<l rend="indent">[Their] fathers go to follow the herd of cows and [their] calves.</l>
<l>You go to abduct the young virgins of the herder village!</l>
<l>Always giving satisfaction to those who are furious, you, herder boy,</l>
<l rend="indent">wander about so that they see you and grumble.</l>
<l>I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
